{"tid":43030,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加：我同哥迪奧拿有相同既足球哲學。","createTime":"2016-12-17T07:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T09:05:01.000Z","uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4da182940341ad9aa990a92d6adfdda5361abb38","tid":43030,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T07:41:07.000Z","msg":"雲加說：「哥帥從巴塞隆拿開始執教，我從青訓開始執教，雖然起點不同，但哥帥非常成功，是最受尊敬的教練之一。他和我很像，他一直努力控制比賽，每個教練都有自己的個性，球隊表現出來的就是教練的個性。」<br />\n「教練是無法複製了，教練只能做自己，他在巴塞受到了告魯夫的影響，當時他還是球員。我認為他有很強的信念，這是作為教練最重要的東西。教練的工作就是要按自己的節奏貫徹自己的哲學，當你去一間新球會，需要分析當下的情況，把你自己的哲學以球員能接受的方式灌輸給球隊。」"},{"pid":"65c0e95c67fb37621fc3b8a2cc58700bac591ac6","tid":43030,"uid":30751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T07:41:39.000Z","msg":"哥狗而家走火入魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56201f9df9b7364fcaf259b41ab4f9ebd3dbb0b","tid":43030,"uid":37168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T07:43:00.000Z","msg":"爺爺竟然將自己同狗相提並論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"709953a77f5a355c8388ada3ba728ba1a900c3b5","tid":43030,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T07:44:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爺爺竟然將自己同狗相提並論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 阿狗咪又係狗"},{"pid":"37026efc5f454da86b4787ef84c2edce6b3441c9","tid":43030,"uid":33719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T07:44:48.000Z","msg":"做乜要同隻狗比?"},{"pid":"4b37ff0e80dd1ae24d24deb9a72b097fa528064a","tid":43030,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T07:44:53.000Z","msg":"人地教左唔夠10年然左，8次頂級聯賽2次歐聯，你70歲都黎連人車尾燈都見唔到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依d死老野真係唔知醜"},{"pid":"e487e8eab1344907afebd244989c30c8e3a4b9d1","tid":43030,"uid":45189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T07:45:06.000Z",